message: I'm feeling generous, but time is money! Let's make a deal.
Come on, Bob! Meet me halfway!
This is my final offer. Take it or leave it.
You said that was your final offer, but I'm not buying it!
Okay Alice, let's be real.  We're running out of time. A 50/50 split is the fairest and fastest way to end this.
Your 50/50 split was a nice try, but I think I can do better!
